{"id": 2413, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果分手也有礼仪，你觉得需要包含哪些内容？", "description": "好聚好散的道理谁都懂，可是该咋做呢？（题图来自：视觉中国 © Stockbyte）", "record_count": 3760, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180611181801MJ6KT3IUZiCyc0Qa.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-12T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 286720, "content": "分手后就干脆的离开对方的生活。通常我们忘不掉的不是那个相爱时对你百依百顺分开后又余情未消的人，而是那个不把你当回事转身离开留下高贵与自尊背影的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 371398}, {"id": 286976, "content": "不诋毁对方，同样祝福对方有个美好的人生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005789}, {"id": 287744, "content": "当面说清楚，不拖泥带水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377140}, {"id": 295425, "content": "我们分手了，但曾经彼此相爱过，你确实对我好，我也会坦城面对彼此的过错，永远承认这段感情，对过去的美好心存感激，哪怕今后是陌生人，我也祝福你未来一切顺利。我会努力向前看，认真生活，依旧相信爱情。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1417486}, {"id": 286722, "content": "面对面沟通，然后好好道个别。", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1371479}, {"id": 289282, "content": "我们已经用恋爱折叠了过去，现在准备用分手描述未来。你准备好了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379658}, {"id": 287235, "content": "自己后悔别迁怒别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374254}, {"id": 286724, "content": "从此山水不相逢，莫道彼此长与短。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372026}, {"id": 287236, "content": "分手见人品 好聚好散", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374263}, {"id": 287748, "content": "分手之后别再别人面前诋毁彼此  不仅是人品问题  毕竟是爱过的人呐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373659}, {"id": 286725, "content": "没有，下一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051333}, {"id": 287237, "content": "可以用一首歌来表达\n“体面”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216290}, {"id": 286727, "content": "不要在分了之后否认前一段关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372035}, {"id": 286728, "content": "说好不联系，就当面互删所有联系方式，彻底一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1296911}, {"id": 286729, "content": "好聚好散", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1358623}, {"id": 286730, "content": "分手后，请把所有的想念烂在肚子里。实在太过于想念了请直接联系前任，不要做太多无谓的东西也不要打扰你朋友的生活。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372039}, {"id": 286986, "content": "你想分手的时候是不想见面的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1194624}, {"id": 286731, "content": "如果非要说起前任，说对方的好话", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274128}, {"id": 286732, "content": "既然选择分手就不要总是回顾", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1016340}, {"id": 288012, "content": "冷静思考。对别人的好要感激，自己做错的要表达歉意。这样做就不会剪不断理还乱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377918}, {"id": 287245, "content": "美丽的开始，清楚的结束。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325388}, {"id": 286734, "content": "分手需要仪式感，不喜欢不爱要说明白，吊着算个什么事儿？还有就是不要捏造事实！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366483}, {"id": 287246, "content": "美丽地开始，清楚地结束。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325388}, {"id": 286735, "content": "分手后就不要做朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372052}, {"id": 287247, "content": "君子断交，不出恶言", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373335}, {"id": 286736, "content": "这两天在好奇心研究所见证了从朋友到热恋到疏远到分手。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141821}, {"id": 287248, "content": "今晚好好地跟他说分手了，不纠缠，不争吵，平静地，就这么分手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326308}, {"id": 292368, "content": "劈腿后他给了我一道道伤，但我流着泪深深感谢他给我的成长。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397988}, {"id": 286993, "content": "分手后请不要和我的朋友在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1354260}, {"id": 286738, "content": "签一份互不打扰的合同吧（母胎单身二十年的小声bb）", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780915}, {"id": 286994, "content": "彼此祝福吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1106994}, {"id": 286739, "content": "怀着念着对方好的心情，分手后也别再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 778732}, {"id": 286740, "content": "什么都说明白点，免得余情未了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372057}, {"id": 286741, "content": "分手炮 最后一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 63, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1204140}, {"id": 286743, "content": "老死不相往来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372058}, {"id": 287768, "content": "提出分手后，另一方不能死缠烂打，影响别人的生活以及人际交往", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377335}, {"id": 286745, "content": "爱不动就爱不动，没什么可解释的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1236016}, {"id": 287257, "content": "认真的说再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374473}, {"id": 286746, "content": "坦白但不争辩……留给分手后的思考！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372065}, {"id": 287258, "content": "当面把一切说的明明白白。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1353891}, {"id": 286747, "content": "明明白白坦坦然然，先扔出结论，我没那么喜欢你了。其余的论点要不要说看情况而定。分手后只有双方都没有感情才能做朋友，如果有一方做不到，不要勉强。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1132734}, {"id": 286748, "content": "尊重彼此选择，并理解安抚对方的感受。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1298517}, {"id": 287260, "content": "祝你有个美好喜乐的人生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1229152}, {"id": 288028, "content": "不会再骚扰你 不会说我舍不得你 我在给你买好吃的 给你打钱 你看我对你多好 你感动了就可以回到我身边 不会再一声不吭的出现在你身边 不会再通过各种社交软件窥探你 知道你交了新男友之后 再来阴阳怪气 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377946}, {"id": 286749, "content": "心平气和的沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1359243}, {"id": 287518, "content": "面对面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254792}, {"id": 286751, "content": "彼此收拾干净整洁大方面对面坐下，诚恳的说清楚分手。有美丽开始，也有端庄的结束。", "image": "img/option/option/20180612124519KRlWZ7Ai6Nt2avzX.jpg", "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372073}, {"id": 286752, "content": "好聚好散。以前相爱过就好，不要去想对方是不是变心了还是怎么滴！你认真去付出过了，对方还是不领情，那就和平分手。用不着记恨……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336453}, {"id": 287008, "content": "你最好能去另一个宇宙", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373141}, {"id": 286753, "content": "承认共同感受到的那些快乐，退回到朋友关系，互相祝愿未来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372081}]}